  "category": "Uncategorized",
  "description": "Fix Typography Issues on Privacy Policy Page\n\nInvestigate and resolve typography-related issues on the privacy policy page at /o-przedszkolu/polityka-prywatnosci/.\n\nRequirements:\n- Review the page at http://localhost:62110/o-przedszkolu/polityka-prywatnosci/ to identify typography problems\n- Address common typography issues such as:\n  - Incorrect font families, weights, or sizes\n  - Poor line height or letter spacing\n  - Inconsistent heading hierarchy\n  - Text overflow or wrapping problems\n  - Incorrect text alignment or justification\n  - Color contrast issues affecting readability\n  - Missing or broken Polish language character support (ą, ć, ę, ł, ń, ó, ś, ź, ż)\n- Ensure typography matches the design system used elsewhere in the application\n- Verify text is readable across different screen sizes (mobile, tablet, desktop)\n- Test with actual Polish content to ensure proper rendering of diacritics\n- Ensure compliance with WCAG accessibility standards for text readability",
